nodes.text: Overhang was a seedy industrial zone in Nexus City, on the planet of Entralla.

Overhang was an industrial center located on the outskirts of Nexus City on the planet of Entralla. Located near the planet's main spaceport, the area was home to many native Entrallans who were employed by the massive transit center or industrial corporations. Because of the Overhang's dense infrastructure, sunlight rarely penetrated down to ground level.
